{"title":"绝不容美帝犯越南","authors":["刘岚山"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":8,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不容美帝犯越南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘岚山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越南的水，越南的山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越南的英雄三千万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三千万人民似钢铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧握着愤怒的枪杆："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国鬼，好大胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你烧掉我一棵草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸死我一头牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每笔血债必须用血还！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越南的山连着中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的水流到越南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中越人民骨肉亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唇齿相依，息息相关："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝在越南点战火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是对中国的侵犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿多人民绝不会坐视，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不容侵略者逞凶作乱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越南的山水连着中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连着整个社会主义阵营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连着全世界人民的心肝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋起的人民千千万万："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯住美国佬的腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把他的魔爪砍断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉紧他颈上的绞索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫世界人民公敌早完蛋！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}